divs: Sighting DetailsDogs were barking, so I walked outside. It was just getting dark and I happened to look up. I saw some strange lights and thought "those aren't stars". Watched the in the east for about 20 minutes until they disappeared over the mountain. *Snow requests that she be assigned to this case.
Summary: Observed unusual lights in the east over the mountains.
